<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="A1">
<sup>*</sup> Department of Internal Medicine, Section of General Medicine, Yale University School of Medicine, New Haven, CT</div>
